title: Ring of Fire - November 23 2013
description:
November 23, 2013
Ring of Fire 
Hosted by Robert F. Kennedy Jr., Mike Papantonio and Sam Seder


This week on Ring of Fire Radio: Senator Bernie Sanders will be here to tell us about his fight for a living wage for American workers.

Lori Wallach from Public Citizen will give us the latest on the Trans Pacific Partnership.

Best-selling author Cliff Schecter will discuss the CBS Benghazi scandal, and how it is the perfect example of the mainstream mediaÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s incompetence.

Rebekah Wilce from the Center for Media and Democracy will explain how a shadowy group called the State Policy Network is pulling the strings for the GOP on the state level.

And blogger Chauncey DeVega will explain how opposition to gun control measures has been linked to racist attitudes.
